<br>
<br>
Also, individuals looking to form groups or just find a group... I'll delete those after a week or two.  The point of this forum is for those running raids to find individuals to fill up the raid.  Not an individual trying to find a group or raid.  I'll leave it up for a few days so you can get with some people but after a week or two I'll remove it.  There just isn't room to have everyone posting here looking for a group.   <p><table><td colspan="2"><td><a href="http://pub5.ezboard.com/fsilentredemptionwebboardfrm19.showMessage?topicID=3.topic"><br>Jaradis Stormcaller</a> - 57th Luminary - Ally to King Tormax of Kael Drakkel<br>
